{
  "stem": "24268.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it happened that I-- they didn't look in my mouth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I took out after, and I sewed up in my little bra.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I had this little ring after the war, until '48.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But obviously, from wearing out and washing, I-- it broke.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And my husband took-- at that time, I was ill-- and took-- I was in hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So he took this and put it in his back pocket.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And obviously, when he pulled out, he forgot, and it was gone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Being in Peterswaldau, when we arrive and the SS took over-- [SIGHS] now this is a-- this is something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They gave us-- [SIGHS] they give us soap to wash, green bars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was a greenish bar-- smelt horrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It wasn't even making any soap, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], but there wasn't no soap.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It says, the lettering, RYF.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That means [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "That means Pure Jewish Fat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "That was made from human, from our people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That's the soap they gave us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[CRYING] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[CRYING] I remained-- I remained there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I took my-- some clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I hid under the straw, [INAUDIBLE] there was straw and burlap wrap, sort of.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I was able to even to have the pillow with my mom's, and me, and all this-- feather blanket, and some clothes-- not all of them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Some I left at the wall-- my raincoat, my other clothes, my summer dresses, and the picture.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was '44 when they-- then I heard, in '43, after the war, somebody in Israel, which was our neighbor, but her parents were the same with us, for the liquidation.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They sent the whole trans-- the whole transport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After she escaped from Auschwitz, she was in music.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
